data.description: This inviting home is nestled on a large and private 1.94-acre lot in a quiet neighborhood. It's also located in the desirable Dorchester II School District. As you arrive, you'll notice a beautiful large yard with mature trees. A new well was installed in June 2021. The attached two-car carport and detached two-car garage/workshop give you plenty of space for parking and storage. A nice screened-in front porch welcomes you home. As you enter, you're greeted by a spacious open floor plan with a great flow for entertaining and everyday living. You'll also find a surround sound system in the home. Enjoy cool evenings in front of the cozy fireplace in the family room. The kitchen offers ample cabinet and counter space.New carpet was installed in the bedrooms in November 2023. The spacious master bedroom features a walk-in closet and a private en suite bathroom. The fenced-in backyard will be perfect for grilling out, entertaining, or watching the kids and/or pets play. You'll also find 2 large sheds in the yard, which provide a great place for storing your tools and lawn equipment. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and Historic Downtown Summerville. Come see your new home, today!
